<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716286943174032183.png" title="1716286943174032183.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 181817.png" width="745" height="458" style="width: 745px; height: 458px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">为深入学习贯彻党的二十大精神，让雷锋精神在新时代绽放更加璀璨的光芒，进一步传承和弘扬雷锋精神，让学雷锋在经管学子中蔚然成风。在2024年3月5日-3月31日，我院团总支结合实际围绕3月5日“学雷锋纪念日”开展 学雷锋主题团日活动---“行摄入微处，携手扬善行”摄影征集主题团日活动，细心观察并用手机或相机捕捉记录身边 的小“雷锋”。他们为大家送去了温暖与关怀，用实际行动传递着爱心与力量。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">迎春启程，向阳而行，奉献之犁，深耕青春，心中有爱，春暖花开。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716287063516003583.png" style="width: 750px; height: 518px;" title="1716287063516003583.png" width="750" height="518"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716287063566058422.png" style="width: 747px; height: 642px;" title="1716287063566058422.png" width="747" height="642"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716287064021059109.png" style="width: 751px; height: 662px;" title="1716287064021059109.png" width="751" height="662"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«劳动最光荣»（崔亦霏摄）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">行如风，助人乐，手留余香，青春当属志愿红。步入大学的第一个雷锋月，我也终于穿上红色马甲为学校和同学做着一件自己力所能及的事情，非常惊喜和感动的是能够被同学记录下来，拍下了这张我学习雷锋的照片，我才发掘其实自己也是生活中的“小雷锋”。青春，沐浴在红热的阳光下，绽放在红艳的花丛中，当志愿为他人服务，建设美好社会。我们每个人都是风华正茂的小小先锋，当一雷锋为精神导向，执使命之火炬，扬青春之“锋”帆。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716287363037087343.png" title="1716287363037087343.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 183009.png" width="754" height="668" style="width: 754px; height: 668px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«我身边的小雷锋»（张俐婷摄）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学雷锋，树新风。下晚自习后，当看教</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px;">到别的室的安全总闸没有关掉时，想到可能会引发的安全隐患，立马就把灯关掉啦！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716287295241060632.png" style="width: 756px; height: 642px;" title="1716287295241060632.png" width="756" height="642"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«我身边的小雷锋»（廖小凤摄）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px;"></span><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716287680628034550.png" title="1716287680628034550.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 181912.png" width="774" height="621" style="width: 774px; height: 621px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«“雷锋”就在我身边»（郑紫馨摄）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">从小事做起，与文明握手学习雷锋，我们班就有这样的同学，她看见教室的灯没有关，会及时的上前关掉。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716287812270093834.png" title="1716287812270093834.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 181919.png" width="790" height="641" style="width: 790px; height: 641px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«传承雷锋精神，不负时代重托»（何轩烨摄）</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">传千年海昏之光之志愿精神</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">奉献之为学校三八妇女节布置场地</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">海昏侯自动售卖机学子风采</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">南青运动会献上自己的力量与温暖的小雷锋们</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716287295792040840.png" style="width: 802px; height: 587px;" title="1716287295792040840.png" width="802" height="587"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716288081018019496.png" style="width: 816px; height: 625px;" title="1716288081018019496.png" width="816" height="625"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716288082584094948.png" style="" title="1716288082584094948.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716288745986012159.png" style="width: 781px; height: 574px;" title="1716288745986012159.png" width="781" height="574"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«学习雷锋的榜样»（陈鑫颖摄）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">经济管理学院门口立牌被大风刮到，将立牌一一扶起来了，我们应传承雷锋精神，绽放时代光芒，我们要把雷锋精神发扬光大，让它成为我们的信仰和追求，从小事做起，用自己的实际行动来践行雷锋精神，让雷锋精神在新时代绽放更加璀璨的光芒。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716288747143083950.png" style="width: 787px; height: 687px;" title="1716288747143083950.png" width="787" height="687"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«学雷锋»（黄阳摄）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">三月春风处处暖，雷锋精神代代传。尽管时代变了，但真善美还在，尽管雷锋走了 ，但“活雷锋”还在，“向上向善好青年”还在。在3月5号雷锋纪念日这天，我参加学院组织的“学雷锋精神，展志愿风采”学院卫生打扫活动。通过参与本次活动，我更加了解了雷锋精神的内涵。在这个过程，我也看到了很多人的善良和爱心。有很多人积极参与了这次活动，用自己的行动表达了雷锋精神的内涵。他们的行动让我深受感动，也让我更加坚定了自己的信念和追求。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716289019111072561.png" title="1716289019111072561.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 185749.png" width="802" height="581" style="width: 802px; height: 581px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 25px 15px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«学雷锋精神，做雷锋青年»（余秘摄）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">三月万物生长好事正酿愿我们的三月日日和煦可盼可期你是人间三月天这一生唯一要完成的KPI就是勇敢大胆爱自己。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">最是一年春光好，植树造林正当时。植树现场一派热火朝天，志愿者们干劲十足，配合默契，分工协作，有的挥锹培土、有的踩实提苗、有的取水浇灌，到处都是忙碌的身影。经过大半天的辛苦，增添了学校的一份绿色，用自己的行动和汗水充分展现了青年的良好风貌与责任担当。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716289217877039678.png" style="width: 836px; height: 372px;" title="1716289217877039678.png" width="836" height="372"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716289220839064888.png" style="width: 841px; height: 575px;" title="1716289220839064888.png" width="841" height="575"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716289221052071643.png" style="width: 846px; height: 569px;" title="1716289221052071643.png" width="846" height="569"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716289221135003775.png" style="width: 856px; height: 573px;" title="1716289221135003775.png" width="856" height="573"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«你是人间三月天»（李妍摄）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">“学雷锋不是喊口号，关键在于行动。”因此，我自愿参加了学院3·12植树节活动，给学院旁的樱花树施肥，用行动守护绿色经管，用行动学习和践行雷锋精神，争做新时代的雷锋青年！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716289514460066964.jpg" title="1716289514460066964.jpg" alt="微信图片_20240521190557.jpg" width="874" height="879" style="width: 874px; height: 879px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">参赛选手作品«三月樱花艳，“锋”暖润心扉»（万俊豪摄）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">“雷锋”不是指一个人 ，而是千千万助人为乐、舍身忘我地奉献的你我。只要我们 愿意伸出援助之手，每一段寻常人生，都能闪耀大爱，每一 束微光，都能汇成炬火温暖人间。通过此次活动，希望让学生们领悟雷锋精神的时代性与永恒性，明白“无论时代如何变迁，雷锋精神永不过时”！</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></p></section></section></section><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p>